## User settings & workspace state
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcuserdatad/
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Build products
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/
Packages/
Package.resolved

