Pods/
Carthage/Build/

## macOS
.DS_Store

## fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png

# The .xcodeproj IS committed (generated from project.yml) so the project
# opens without XcodeGen. Ignore only its per-user state:
UsageMonitor.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
UsageMonitor.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
UsageMonitor.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/IDEWorkspaceChecks.plist
